Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:17.33,para-internal,S,0,0,0,,Hádam to viem rozoznať.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:20.06,para-internal,S,0,0,0,,Ale... Migi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:22.58,para-internal,S,0,0,0,,Spi!
